Class CardInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • CardInfo

  • public class CardInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class CardInfo stores primitive datas for each specific card. accountName stores the name of the card owner. company stores the name of the card company. date stores the date the card was opened. lastBalance stores the balance of the card. accountStatus stores how long the account's been overdue.
    Author:
    Sam
